10 ounce Ground Beef
4 ounce Ricotta Cheese
1 ounce Parmesan Cheese
1.25 ounce Artichoke Hearts
¾ teaspoon Italian Herb & Red Pepper Blend
6.5 ounce Riced Cauliflower
½ ounce Roasted Almonds
2.75 ounce Kale
2.25 ounce Sunflower Basil Sauce
Cooking Oil
Olive Oil
Salt
Pepper

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.